					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">It's because $2006 is actually a $2005 write in a way...it's confusing. But to avoid it perfect, write to $2000 and $2005 (2 times) to make sure it doesn't happen. If you wanna know why, see <a href="http://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/The_skinny_on_NES_scrolling" class="postlink">The skinny on NES scrolling</a>.</div>

